Package ohos.ai.cv.common

Class CvRect

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.ai.cv.common.CvRect
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Sequenceable

    public class CvRect
extends Object
implements Sequenceable
    Describes the rectangle area of images.

    The rectangle area has four coordinates (in pixels): vertical coordinate of the upper boundary, horizontal coordinate of the left boundary, vertical coordinate of the lower boundary, and horizontal coordinate of the right boundary.

    Since:
    1
